# Direct LayerZero VT API key. WARNING: any var prefixed with VITE_ is
# inlined into the client JS shipped to every visitor — anyone can read it
# in devtools. This pattern is fine for local development and personal demos
# only. For anything reachable from the public internet, use the
# `privy-next-serverless` example instead, which keeps the key server-side.
VITE_VT_API_KEY=
